title: Vung Tau
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A Vietnamese restaurant where the atmosphere is usually loud and lively. Offers a separate vegetarian menu upon request which includes several appetizers and main meals. Try the com tay cam clay pot rice which is fragranced rice cooked in a clay pot with veggie ham. The parking lot is limited and can be full during the weekends.
